    <h2>Tools for Creating Infographics</h2>
    <p>Engaging in an infographic project provides hands-on familiarity with essential tools like <strong>Canva</strong> and <strong>Venngage</strong>, offering an opportunity to harness creativity in presenting data in visually captivating, impactful, and efficient ways.</p>
    
    <img src="https://dt2sdf0db8zob.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/infographic-templates_1200x630-840x430.png" alt="Infographic Tools">

    <h2>Why Use Infographics?</h2>
    <p>Infographics are powerful tools because they make complex information easily digestible. They attract and hold the audience's attention, making the communication of data more effective.</p>
